# BankingAppV2

A web-based banking application built with Django, which allows users to register accounts, view balances, deposit, and withdraw money. The project leverages a PostgreSQL database and is hosted on Heroku.

## Features
- User authentication (login, registration)
- Deposit and withdrawal functionality
- Viewing and updating account balance
- User profile with address information
- Admin interface for managing users and transactions

## Technologies Used
- Django (Backend)
- PostgreSQL (Database)
- Heroku (Deployment)
- HTML, CSS, JavaScript (Frontend)
